'''Truphone'''是一家跨國[[移動網絡運營商|移動網絡運營商]]，總部位於英國[[倫敦|倫敦]]，此外在[[美國|美國]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]和[[香港|香港]]等多國和地區有辦公處。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.truphone.com/ROW/About-us/Our-Offices/ |title=Truphone, Office locations |accessdate=2014-09-02 |archive-date=2013-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020185551/http://www.truphone.com/ROW/About-us/Our-Offices/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該公司在2006年由詹姆斯·塔格（James Tagg）、[[亞歷山大·斯特勞布|亞歷山大·斯特勞布]]（Alexander Straub）和阿里斯泰爾·坎貝爾（Alistair Campbell）成立。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.realwire.com/release_detail.asp?ReleaseID=4909 |title=Truphone brings internet-rate phone calls to ordinary mobiles at The Cloud’s hotspots |work=RealWire |date=2006-12-06 |accessdate=2012-02-13 |archive-date=2012-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406125904/http://www.realwire.com/release_detail.asp?ReleaseID=4909 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

